ZH: 边境是两个国家之间的界限。
EN: The border is the boundary between two countries.

ZH: 山区和平原之间有一条边境河流。
EN: There is a border river between the mountainous area and the plain.

ZH: 这个城市靠近国家的边境。
EN: This city is close to the country's border.

ZH: 我们需要过边境检查才能进入那个国家。
EN: We need to go through border control to enter that country.

ZH: 边境地区是贸易的重要通道。
EN: Border areas are important channels for trade.

ZH: 在边境警察的指导下，我们成功通过了边境。
EN: with the guidance of the border police, we successfully crossed the border.

ZH: 这片边境地区风景优美。
EN: The scenery in this border area is beautiful.

ZH: 边境上有一片广阔的平原。
EN: There is a vast plain along the border.

ZH: 我们在边境上建立了一座观光塔。
EN: We built a sightseeing tower on the border.

ZH: 该地区的安全形势一直很紧张，因为靠近边境。
EN: The security situation in the area has always been tense because it is close to the border.

ZH: 我的家乡位于两个国家的边境。
EN: My hometown is located on the border between two countries.

ZH: 这条公路与边境平行。
EN: This road runs parallel to the border.

ZH: 边境线上有很多国旗。
EN: There are many national flags along the border line.

ZH: 边境地区需要加强军事防御。
EN: The border areas need to strengthen military defense.

ZH: 这个村庄靠近边境，所以地势相对较高。
EN: This village is close to the border, so the terrain is relatively high.

ZH: 这个小镇的居民与邻国有着紧密的边境联系。
EN: The residents of this town have close border connections with the neighboring country.

ZH: 我们需要办理边境通行证才能进入那个区域。
EN: We need to obtain a border pass to enter that region.

ZH: 边境地区的居民可以享受跨境购物的便利。
EN: Residents in border areas can enjoy the convenience of cross-border shopping.

ZH: 他们在边境一带居住已有多年。
EN: They have been living in the border area for many years.

ZH: 边境上的贸易活动对两国经济都起着重要作用。
EN: Trade activities on the border play an important role in the economies of both countries.
